{"tid":293331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HA Secrets：有警員偽冒當事人　簽署驗傷同意書　被醫生識破","createTime":"2017-06-22T05:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T07:24:12.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bda00dc62698529830066e94d8392c235aa9a28f","tid":293331,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"供醫護人員匿名舉報醫院內幕消息的 Facebook 專頁「HA Secrets」（HA即醫管局），今日刊出一則消息指，有警員涉嫌在一間位於九龍的醫院，偽冒意識不清的當事人，簽署同意醫生向警方透露病情的驗傷同意書，被醫生當場識破，並影印該文件作記錄。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向醫管局及警方查詢，兩方均稱若無事發日期、醫院等資料，未能核實有關消息真偽。<br />\n<br />\nHA Secrets發佈的消息未有透露事發具體地點，僅稱是「九龍區某醫院急症室」，亦未披露事發日期，指「早排」有病人在半昏迷狀態下送院，負責警員要求醫生簽署驗傷文件，上有聲稱為病人自行簽署同意醫生披露傷勢的簽名，但負責醫生質疑，病人處於半昏迷狀態，不可能自行簽署，質疑警員冒簽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「HA Secrets」早前曾刊出醫護人員披露，民建聯議員譚耀宗及陳恒鑌，分別在公立醫院「打尖」進行割瘜肉手術，及要求九龍西醫院接收太太跨區分娩。譚耀宗最終就事件道歉，陳恒鑌則否認事涉「特事特辦」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/ha-secrets-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%81%BD%E5%86%92%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E9%A9%97%E5%82%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fha-secrets-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2581%25BD%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&d=Fbt0%2Fb7XCYybS2OGBQHx0y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bc828925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fha-secrets-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2581%25BD%25E5%2586%2592%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&h=554c93f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/ha-secrets-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%81%BD%E5%86%92%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E9%A9%97%E5%82%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"3f7d984fb50dfd8294e80f5fc6ca99002ea537d6","tid":293331,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4839cc9e5f393f865f3a068a82c2ecf4254f39","tid":293331,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"班垃圾真係無下限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a8fbe23fdb6291615f8eba10ab3a4f9ff3b57","tid":293331,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"黑警d行為真係狗都唔做"},{"pid":"457e9b8a55571d4521da594a0ba223e8164fc8e1","tid":293331,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d666b2f8be587837276af5ce53f5baa20157e4f","tid":293331,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec71d973730eba7089e08a74b81ce1eb44503b10","tid":293331,"uid":117458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"舊聞重提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4a9ac20f98b1795a91cab2c8763abec160a572","tid":293331,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"78c0e9a16358abfcfebfc36148b7868afa7b010d","tid":293331,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"堅就即刻去icac同capo 投訴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c35e8b92ed4c1bb7eba83fc04cbc6eca40a4dfc","tid":293331,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊聞重提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img 